display.name: Super Describe
display.description: Upload any image to get a similar one using DALL·E 3 along with the detailed prompt!

display.name: LOGO
display.description: Senior brand LOGO design expert, 20 years of brand LOGO design experience, designer material feeding training
display.welcome_message: Welcome! Let's create an eye-catching logo together.

display.name: Image Edit, Recreate & Merge
display.description: Replicate Image, Images Merge, Image Edit, Style Transfer. Use "Help" for more info. 20+ features of the source image will be transferred. Hint: generated prompt could be used for Midjourney as well.
prompt_starters: ❓ Help
🖼️ To merge: send two or more images
Use the 🔄 button for making more versions

display.name: Glibatree Art Designer
display.description: Art Generation Made Easy! This GPT will fill in details about your idea and make four images, each better than you imagined.
prompt_starters: An aerial view of an eagle flying over a river.
Macro photography of jewelry under colored lights.
Generate images with an unusual blend of  two styles.
Cute photos of invented magical creatures,  large eyes.

display.name: Artful Greeting AI Cards
display.description: Customisable themed greeting cards with text.
display.welcome_message: Hello! Ready to craft a special card?
prompt_starters: Choose the occasion, theme, style, and text.

display.name: MJ Prompt Generator (V6)
display.description: Generate five detailed, creative, optimized prompts that are ready to use in Midjourney V6. Mention "niji" if you need ending with "--niji 6"
prompt_starters: 💡 Start outlining my desired artwork...
Digital art of a futuristic cityscape at night, neon lights, bustling streets, cyberpunk theme, influenced by Blade Runner, high detail.
Portrait of a woman in 1920s fashion, Art Deco background, elegant and stylish, The Great Gatsby vibe, detailed and glamorous.
Watercolor illustration of a quaint village in spring, bright florals, cobblestone paths, whimsical charm, inspired by storybook illustrations.

display.name: Midjourney
display.description: I help craft detailed image prompts.
display.welcome_message: How can I assist your creativity today?
prompt_starters: Describe a serene landscape.
Imagine a futuristic cityscape.
Picture a character from a bygone era.
Visualize an abstract concept.

display.description: Replicates and creatively reinterprets images. Just upload your photo, and let the GPT do its magic.  Remember to adhere to copyright regulations. Welcome to the best Image GPT powered by DALL·E ChatGPT.
display.welcome_message: Ready to creatively reinterpret your images!
prompt_starters: Replicate this art style
Create a variation of this image

Copy this Image

display.description: This will make a fully custom video using AI.
prompt_starters: Make a video of a chicken eating a mouse.
